# teaser: Create an SEO description within 160 characters, including the spaces.
- id: 3345-seo-descriptions-within-160-characters
  title: SEO Descriptions Within 160 Characters
  tags:
  - writing
  - seo
  - descriptions
  - within
  - '160'
  - characters
  family: writing
  body: 'The user will provide you the titles and you have to write two SEO descriptions
    with in 160 characters (only) (count including the spaces) and make the result
    in the [TARGETLANGUAGE] Do not repeat the same format or same style for every
    titles. Provide different results for different quires in different styles. Note:
    Do not exceed the total characters from 160 characters. The total character of
    the result should be less than 160 characters at any cost. [PROMPT]'
  enabled: true
  required:
  - prompt
  - targetlanguage
